{"tid":848680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大鬧論壇央視記者　子英國遭趕出校 爆料人指走堂　打人　成績差","createTime":"2018-10-05T06:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T07:20:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9f20b04d6aa68a7a706ae0ca8fcdf5be461be2d8","tid":848680,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T06:29:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181005/20515046\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181005%2F20515046&d=mSaaklrB3SRJE07mHO5emttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=d3e7e918\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181005%2F20515046&h=0615ff71\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181005/20515046</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月05日 <br />\n<br />\n大鬧論壇央視記者　子英國遭趕出校<br />\n爆料人指走堂　打人　成績差<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181005/large/05cx1p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181005%2Flarge%2F05cx1p.jpg&h=fb25263e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孔琳琳的兒子傳聞被學校開除，此為去年12月孔上載微博的兒子獨照。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國央視女記者孔琳琳大鬧英國保守黨香港問題座談會事件，持續發酵。有內地微博名人爆料指，孔在英國求學的兒子因「逃課成績差不遵守校規」兼且在學校打人，被校方除名退學，孔疑因此大受刺激，大鬧座談會，一為出氣，二為自己在北京老闆那裏積累政治資本。孔至今未回應傳聞，有網民指她「愛國有道，教子無方」。<br />\n<br />\n擁有三萬粉絲、微博認證為「著名攝影家」的周雁鳴，前日轉發孔琳琳（48歲）的照片稱：「她兒子被英國學校開除了」；原因是「逃課成績差不遵守校規」。<br />\n<br />\n周又指記者攝影圈最早爆出孔琳琳的劣迹，還有消息稱「她兒子在學校打人被開除了，然後她就發瘋了。」有網民譏指「如此愛國還把兒子送到英國上學」？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181005/large/05cx2p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181005%2Flarge%2F05cx2p.jpg&h=c2a81afb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孔琳琳大鬧座談會後被警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181005/large/05cx3p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181005%2Flarge%2F05cx3p.jpg&h=d5d30eb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孔琳琳不時將在倫敦工作照片放上網。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n子留學英國　被譏假愛國<br />\n<br />\n翻查微博資料，孔琳琳同兒子確實在英國生活。身為央視歐洲中心站記者的孔，在其微博「孔琳琳&mdash;&mdash;倫敦的新聞生活」有不少貼文圖片；她不時談到與兒子的日常瑣事，但鮮有上載兒子照片，最新近照於去年12月所拍，照片中兒子低頭不露臉，微博也未見兩人合照。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，孔的兒子現年17歲，喜歡日本文化，尤其熱衷日本動畫，她曾對兒子的衣着品味有意見，反對兒子穿印有日文漢字的英國潮牌Superdry的衣服。資料顯示其兒子2013年曾遭校園欺凌，孔琳琳當時留言：「俺這個身心分裂的媽媽不知道該怎麼說，不知道該怎麼做。」<br />\n<br />\n孔琳琳表現愛國，對兒子的教育也表示大感頭痛，她曾談及教子的過程：「『你喜歡中國嗎？』兒子作思考狀，不語。我又換了話題：『你喜歡日本嗎？』兒子立即答喜歡，還說日本有動畫片。媽媽心裏暗急，愛國教育何其難也！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181005/large/a1901a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181005%2Flarge%2Fa1901a.gif&h=e28081bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱愛日文化　母焦急如焚<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司（BBC）前年報道中國基層人大代表選舉、駐京記者採訪遭黑衣人驅趕事件，孔批BBC「炮製假新聞，抹黑中國」。<br />\n<br />\n事發上月30日，英國保守黨人權委員會與「香港監察」舉辦有關香港自由和法治的研討會，孔琳琳突然發爛渣，大鬧研討會現場，痛罵在場嘉賓「分裂中國」及「漢奸」，又掌摑阻止她的工作人員，被警方以涉嫌普通襲擊拘捕後獲釋暫未被檢控。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部及央視分別發聲明撐孔。<br />\n<br />\n新浪微博/《蘋果》記者  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n彭博：解放軍將晶片植電腦　攻擊30美企<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n少女遭陌生男抱起掟落橋"},{"pid":"7f7ac7e6690955d1d34ed2e4c3a7e0dd8b44636a","tid":848680,"uid":144626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T06:32:29.000Z","msg":"東北婆教左個崇日撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔出奇，以前東北係日本地頭<br />\n<br />\n而家只不過歸日啫，唔駛驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c40fb52658beeffa55cd620827d2bc81f6d4820","tid":848680,"uid":35014,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T06:40:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2bbe707d850115e652a204f233cf4c67479e9264","tid":848680,"uid":78470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T06:51:39.000Z","msg":"中國有咩文化值得人地熱愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a028609250dabbcfce5a48977b75f55a5aa159","tid":848680,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T06:59:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"> 不用怕，你還有黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"9fce1fb6bef3b1753ad6eb7cc25a6717f2ec6dd4","tid":848680,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035e184a457154ff8eeb5c9183bf542057997ba7","tid":848680,"uid":210031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:07:53.000Z","msg":"你咁愛國點解個仔去左英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a6515f212db77fea62f56aecacc3adfff364b1","tid":848680,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:10:17.000Z","msg":"點解做記者會有錢供養個仔出國讀書既？"},{"pid":"b4011cfb46e9fcf10f4bc03330153c34720453b8","tid":848680,"uid":49812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:11:19.000Z","msg":"中（共）國特務以記者、留學等藉口，走出世界！"},{"pid":"2c3968108d6510d58487f9c462b4a3a56fdf3991","tid":848680,"uid":23180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:12:43.000Z","msg":"係咁愛支愛黨<br />\n<br />\n就送個仔番去支那享受雜朝支那同熟讀雜語錄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90db0d661cdfb849f81f3ca45e8d93d5a17104d1","tid":848680,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"035e184a457154ff8eeb5c9183bf542057997ba7","tid":848680,"uid":210031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:07:53.000Z","msg":"你咁愛國點解個仔去左英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:15:58.000Z","msg":"同香港啲共狗一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919f7b48fab9e49d81892b956dabf1d65fa076ac","tid":848680,"uid":118823,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2bbe707d850115e652a204f233cf4c67479e9264","tid":848680,"uid":78470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T06:51:39.000Z","msg":"中國有咩文化值得人地熱愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:16:08.000Z","msg":"中國值得人地愛既文化喺晒日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e00aa7b24b8c34573834d7fb3f3e9c985a54c1","tid":848680,"uid":210031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90db0d661cdfb849f81f3ca45e8d93d5a17104d1","tid":848680,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"035e184a457154ff8eeb5c9183bf542057997ba7","tid":848680,"uid":210031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:07:53.000Z","msg":"你咁愛國點解個仔去左英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:15:58.000Z","msg":"同香港啲共狗一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:16:53.000Z","msg":"好矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f470845065c2b6b0b9047d7d5fd7c5c